title: Episode 167: The 5 Year Plan (Feat. Riff Raff)
itunes:title: Episode 167: The 5 Year Plan (Feat. Riff Raff)
description:
Rapper Riff Raff, AKA Jody Highroller joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and opens up about his past relationships, including his trust issues. Riff Raff breaks down his 5 year rule regarding dating, and much more! Enjoy!
